        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Scutopus hamatanii sp. nov. Sclerites of holotype. (A, B) peribuccal region; (C–F) in foregut region; (G–H) at ventral suture; (I) in anterior midgut sac region; (J) in posterior midgut sac region; (K) in prepallial region; (L) inside of posterior margin of pallial region; (M) at posterior margin of pallial region. Long scale bar (left): 100 µm for A–L; Short scale bar (right): 100 µm for M." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4607719/files/figure.png" .

