<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4607717>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Scutopus hamatanii sp. nov. (A) holotype, NSMT-Mo 78601, preserved condition; (B) paratype 5, NSMT-Mo 78606, preserved condition; (C) pedal shield of holotype; (D–G) radula of holotype: (D) lateral view with anteriorly protruding end of radula membrane; (E) dorsal view; (F, G) close up of teeth. Scale bars: 0.5 mm for A, B; 200 µm for C–E; 50 µm for F, G." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4607717/files/figure.png" .

